Pundi XPOS

We continue to improve, refine and optimize the hardware, software and security of our POS solution to maintain the best in class quality. You can utilize XPOS to offer crypto exchange service in physical shops, accept crypto payment, provide crypto remittance, or tokenize your loyalty points subject to local regulations.

Contact us

Worlds 1st music festival powered by XPOS

Instant Transactions

XPOS transactions happen instantly at less than 0.5 seconds. No delays. Just pay and go.

Support Multiple Cross-Chain Digital Currencies

The XPOS is digital currency neutral, so you can transact with your favorite coins or tokens like BTC, ETH, BNB, PUNDIX, etc.

Top Up Digital Currency With Ease

In addition to making payment, customers can acquire digital currencies like Bitcoin from the XPOS with ease. The experience is as easy as buying a cup of coffee.

Stable Coin Settlement without Volatility

To avoid any volatility risk, merchants will receive their settlement in stable currency (or Fiat in partnership with their distribution partners).

Location of Featured XPOS Merchants

Located in the map is a list of our featured XPOS merchants. If you are one of our distribution partners or individual XPOS merchants, please submit your location details and we will add them to the map.

Hardware Wallet Card

Pundi X supports web3 transactions from the self-custodial hardware wallet card. Businesses can grow their community and customer base with web3 empowered card-based loyalty program by creating NFT or tokenize their loyalty points to offer discounts and membership benefits by issuing the customized hardware wallet card with your brand on it!

To learn more, visit https://pxcard.io/customization
